[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_large.png?m=1775086598", "name": "promotions", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_normal.png?m=1775086598", "title": "推广", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions", "topics": 10929, "footer": "", "header": "来自厂商的推广活动类主题，会被归类到这个节点。希望有情怀的产商们在发布推广内容时，主动选择发布到本节点下。点击 <a href=\"/help/node\">这里</a> 阅读 V2EX 的节点使用指南。", "title_alternative": "Promotions", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1775086598", "stars": 1160, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 864, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 784390, "username": "Unity2Ai", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Unity2Ai", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_mini.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_normal.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_large.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_xlarge.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_xxlarge.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_xxxlarge.png?m=1774866401", "created": 1768478081, "last_modified": 1774866401, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "npe", "last_touched": 1775109391, "title": "大模型中转站， Unity2.Ai 内测招募：直达源头，拒绝“掺水”！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202897", "created": 1775039328, "deleted": 0, "content": "# 🚀 Unity2.Ai 内测招募：直达源头，拒绝“掺水”！\r\n\r\n**为什么选择我们？** 直达源头，从根本上杜绝降智与回复干预。\r\n\r\n受够了模型降智和回复“掺水”？**Unity2.Ai** 正式开启周末公测，诚邀硬核玩家入驻！\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 💰 极具竞争力的计费\r\n* **全站汇率：** 1 人民币 = 1 美元\r\n* **核心定价：**\r\n    * **ccmax:** 2.5 元/刀\r\n    * **codex:** 0.4 元/刀\r\n\r\n### 🎁 限时内测福利\r\n* **注册即送：** 完成注册，回帖报上 ID ，并加入官方群。\r\n* **到账奖励：** 群内报上您的注册邮箱，**立赠 $10 体验金！**\r\n* **无门槛使用：** 全模型覆盖，真实额度，直接起飞。\r\n\r\n### 💎 为什么选择 Unity2.Ai ？\r\n1.  **直达 CCMAX 源头**：跳过层层转包，享受最原汁原味的响应速度与稳定性。\r\n2.  **绝不“掺水”**：承诺不进行任何模型降智或低价模型替换，拒绝后台逻辑干预，还原真实模型智商。\r\n3.  **极简接入**：支持标准 OpenAI 、Anthropic 格式，一键替换 API 基地址，完美适配各种插件与 IDE 工具。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 🏃 如何参与？\r\n1.  🔗 [点击此处前往注册]( https://unity2.ai/register?ref=OinayD4S) \r\n2.  📧 **群内发送：** 报邮箱：`yourname@email.com` 或 用户 ID\r\n3.  **等待后台手动充值后，即可开始巅峰测试！**\r\n\r\n> **提示：** 注册后进群或者回帖发送您的 ID ，即可申请 10 刀免费额度。\r\n\r\n\r\nID 获取的方式，注册后点击左上角 复制我的 id 即可\r\n\r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/11inRNp.png)", "content_rendered": "<h1>🚀 <a href=\"http://Unity2.Ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unity2.Ai</a> 内测招募：直达源头，拒绝“掺水”！</h1>\n<p><strong>为什么选择我们？</strong> 直达源头，从根本上杜绝降智与回复干预。</p>\n<p>受够了模型降智和回复“掺水”？<strong><a href=\"http://Unity2.Ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unity2.Ai</a></strong> 正式开启周末公测，诚邀硬核玩家入驻！</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3>💰 极具竞争力的计费</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>全站汇率：</strong> 1 人民币 = 1 美元</li>\n<li>\n<strong>核心定价：</strong><ul>\n<li><strong>ccmax:</strong> 2.5 元/刀</li>\n<li><strong>codex:</strong> 0.4 元/刀</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎁 限时内测福利</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>注册即送：</strong> 完成注册，回帖报上 ID ，并加入官方群。</li>\n<li><strong>到账奖励：</strong> 群内报上您的注册邮箱，<strong>立赠 $10 体验金！</strong></li>\n<li><strong>无门槛使用：</strong> 全模型覆盖，真实额度，直接起飞。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>💎 为什么选择 <a href=\"http://Unity2.Ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unity2.Ai</a> ？</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>直达 CCMAX 源头</strong>：跳过层层转包，享受最原汁原味的响应速度与稳定性。</li>\n<li><strong>绝不“掺水”</strong>：承诺不进行任何模型降智或低价模型替换，拒绝后台逻辑干预，还原真实模型智商。</li>\n<li><strong>极简接入</strong>：支持标准 OpenAI 、Anthropic 格式，一键替换 API 基地址，完美适配各种插件与 IDE 工具。</li>\n</ol>\n<hr/>\n<h3>🏃 如何参与？</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>🔗 <a href=\"https://unity2.ai/register?ref=OinayD4S\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击此处前往注册</a> </li>\n<li>📧 <strong>群内发送：</strong> 报邮箱：<code>yourname@email.com</code> 或 用户 ID</li>\n<li><strong>等待后台手动充值后，即可开始巅峰测试！</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>提示：</strong> 注册后进群或者回帖发送您的 ID ，即可申请 10 刀免费额度。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>ID 获取的方式，注册后点击左上角 复制我的 id 即可</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/11inRNp.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1775039536, "replies": 240, "id": 1202897}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10471, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2241, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 477690, "username": "HOmo00", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/HOmo00", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_mini.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_normal.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_large.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_xlarge.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_xxlarge.png?m=1680250784", "created": 1584629141, "last_modified": 1680250784, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "7beloved", "last_touched": 1775108522, "title": "同事想和你打扑克的话，你们会和同事打扑克吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202793", "created": 1775023842, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1775023842, "replies": 149, "id": 1202793}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 237949, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->"