false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 666086, "username": "kcerty", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kcerty", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_mini.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_normal.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_large.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_xlarge.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_xxlarge.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_xxxlarge.png?m=1703130789", "created": 1701940561, "last_modified": 1703130789, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "kcerty", "last_touched": 1775108451, "title": "假如喜欢孩子，但不敢结婚有什么办法呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202792", "created": 1775023807, "deleted": 0, "content": "在网上看了很多人发的帖子，婚后一地鸡毛。以前也向往组建幸福美满的家庭，但是看到大多数人不幸，同时自己喜欢小孩子，所以萌生出一个想法。\r\n\r\n如果自己有点钱，可以花钱买卵子，然后去境外找人代孕，总花费 50W 左右吧？这样既不用考虑婚后一地鸡毛，随时可能被分 50%还要带走孩子的情况，也可以实现自己想要孩子的结果，而且成本比结婚还要低一些。\r\n\r\n问题就是孩子出生在单亲家庭，但这情况似乎越来越多了，也不算很稀奇吧？另一个就是孩子带回来是否合法的问题，要怎么操作？\r\n\r\n这只是突发奇想，特别是看到时不时有老哥被爆金币，看的我都害怕了。", "content_rendered": "<p>在网上看了很多人发的帖子，婚后一地鸡毛。以前也向往组建幸福美满的家庭，但是看到大多数人不幸，同时自己喜欢小孩子，所以萌生出一个想法。</p>\n<p>如果自己有点钱，可以花钱买卵子，然后去境外找人代孕，总花费 50W 左右吧？这样既不用考虑婚后一地鸡毛，随时可能被分 50%还要带走孩子的情况，也可以实现自己想要孩子的结果，而且成本比结婚还要低一些。</p>\n<p>问题就是孩子出生在单亲家庭，但这情况似乎越来越多了，也不算很稀奇吧？另一个就是孩子带回来是否合法的问题，要怎么操作？</p>\n<p>这只是突发奇想，特别是看到时不时有老哥被爆金币，看的我都害怕了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775025924, "replies": 89, "id": 1202792}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_large.png?m=1643940920", "name": "ev", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_normal.png?m=1643940920", "title": "电动汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ev", "topics": 425, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "EV", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_mini.png?m=1643940920", "stars": 434, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1034, "parent_node_name": "tech"}, "member": {"id": 665411, "username": "lifeOsDeveloper", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lifeOsDeveloper", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_mini.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_normal.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_large.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_xlarge.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_xxlarge.png?m=1710487464", "created": 1701485028, "last_modified": 1710487464, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ltmst", "last_touched": 1775109511, "title": "买特斯拉还是小鹏，听说小鹏 vla2.0 很强", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202993", "created": 1775092518, "deleted": 0, "content": "model y / 小鹏 p7", "content_rendered": "<p>model y / 小鹏 p7</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775093091, "replies": 84, "id": 1202993}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_large.png?m=1542423096", "name": "guangzhou", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_normal.png?m=1542423096", "title": "广州", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou", "topics": 1511, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Guangzhou", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096", "stars": 1512, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 20, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 622125, "username": "CaptainLee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/CaptainLee", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ed2727ceb88231b89961265e574b454?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ed2727ceb88231b89961265e574b454?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ed2727ceb88231b89961265e574b454?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1680448221, "last_modified": 1680448221, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "LamKingTak", "last_touched": 1775109309, "title": "该不该现在买房？各位帮忙参谋参谋！由于房贷是刚性的，在 AI 趋势下后期工资能否覆盖房贷", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202999", "created": 1775093266, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：\r\n本人：东莞上班，小公司上班，传统行业 IT ，公司业务竞争大；老婆锂电池公司销售，工作压力大；年综合收入 40 左右，一个一岁半小孩；感觉这两份工作都不稳定；担心 AI 发展浪潮下，后期都找不到工作，无法还款房贷；刚刚又看到甲骨文裁员那么多，东莞也没什么 IT 工作可以找；\r\n房子：\r\n东莞市中心，房龄 20 年，4 楼，总价 230 ，需要贷款 90 ；然后还要后期装修；可以公积金贷款；距离我们上班都是 30min 车程；看房看了半年了；家里人也是想买，现在租房；\r\n\r\n各位给给建议，该不该买房，今晚要去中介房主聊价格了；心里还是有点担忧后期失业没有钱还房贷；先谢谢各位了！", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：\n本人：东莞上班，小公司上班，传统行业 IT ，公司业务竞争大；老婆锂电池公司销售，工作压力大；年综合收入 40 左右，一个一岁半小孩；感觉这两份工作都不稳定；担心 AI 发展浪潮下，后期都找不到工作，无法还款房贷；刚刚又看到甲骨文裁员那么多，东莞也没什么 IT 工作可以找；\n房子：\n东莞市中心，房龄 20 年，4 楼，总价 230 ，需要贷款 90 ；然后还要后期装修；可以公积金贷款；距离我们上班都是 30min 车程；看房看了半年了；家里人也是想买，现在租房；</p>\n<p>各位给给建议，该不该买房，今晚要去中介房主聊价格了；心里还是有点担忧后期失业没有钱还房贷；先谢谢各位了！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775104498, "replies": 75, "id": 1202999}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 70393, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9617, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 770709, "username": "AnQiYang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/AnQiYang", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "t